	measure 'Available Capacity' = ```
			
			VAR _totalusers = 
			    CALCULATE(
			        DISTINCTCOUNT(dim_users[User_ID])
			    )
			VAR _workingdays =
			    (CALCULATE(
			        DISTINCTCOUNT('dim_date'[Date]),
			        'dim_date'[Holiday Type] <> "Fixed Leave",
			        dim_date[IsWeekday] = TRUE()
			    ))
			RETURN _totalusers * _workingdays * 9
			```
		formatString: #,0
		displayFolder: # Grand Totals
		lineageTag: 53ce363f-31d8-4c59-b97f-e4dece5c7298

